creator: Norman Duncan
description:
LibriVox recording of The Measure Of A Man; A Tale Of The Big Woods by Norman Duncan.
Read in English by David Wales

A tale of a singular man at work among lumber-jacks. Duncan's droll style and tongue-in-cheek viewpoint keep the reader and listener much entertained. - Summary by Book preface and david wales

For further information, including links to online text, reader information, RSS feeds, CD cover or other formats (if available), please go to the LibriVox catalog page for this recording.

For more free audio books or to become a volunteer reader, visit LibriVox.org.

Download M4B (215MB)
